Notebook
Tatanggap: Kim Yumi

596
00:45:10,230 --> 00:45:12,040
Oh, tama.

597
00:45:12,040 --> 00:45:15,640
Nang matapos niya ang libro, may kailangan muna siyang gawin.

598
00:45:20,500 --> 00:45:21,540
Ano ito?

599
00:45:21,540 --> 00:45:23,980
[Laptop]

600
00:45:23,980 --> 00:45:25,240
Hello.

601
00:45:25,240 --> 00:45:28,870
Wung. Bakit ka nagpadala ng laptop?

602
00:45:28,870 --> 00:45:31,080
Oh! Dumating na?

603
00:45:31,080 --> 00:45:33,950
Sabi mo nawala sayo. Akala ko kakailanganin mo agad.

604
00:45:33,950 --> 00:45:35,200
Hindi ka marunong sa teknolohiya.

605
00:45:35,200 --> 00:45:41,100
Teka ... Wung, nagpapasalamat ako, ngunit natagpuan ko ang aking laptop.

606
00:45:41,100 --> 00:45:43,620
Oh, talaga? Magaling yan.

607
00:45:43,620 --> 00:45:45,840
